Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:10.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:15.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:19.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to give you \Nup to anyone... Anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:23.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make you king of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:33.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All for the the World of Great Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:18.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the both of us will...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:22.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you stopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:24.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A dead end?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:27.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:29.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ark of Embodiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your brain made of muscle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Try thinking about {\i1}where {\i0}\Nyou're escaping to next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:43.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Clam it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:46.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How 'bout you try runnin' yourself next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:50.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've taken a lot of damage! \NI can just now barely stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:53.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You still seem plenty kickin' to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:58.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:03:01.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that thing goes wild like it did \Nbefore, this cliff is gonna break quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As for me, I can fly. But, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We could do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:13.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:17.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew those glasses you wear make you smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:22.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look here... I'm smart \Neven without the glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:24.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Among all the Fairies, I'm the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So there you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:26.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:28.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:31.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, big-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:38.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have a head-to-head \Nbattle, Man-to-Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now bring it on, fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:46.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Over: Beast Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:49.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:57.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:00.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about that? Worked like a cha-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:08.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go making me the decoy \Njust 'cause I can fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:13.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The communication between two lovers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:15.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...sometimes goes hand-in-hand \Nwith a violent skinship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:16.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:23.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well in defeating my Sacred \NGuardian Beast, Thunderclap Belcusas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:29.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You truly showed me well your \Npitiful struggle against death...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:35.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you fight with not even a hint of \Nelegance, unbefitting of a wizard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:37.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:39.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm going to puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in the World of Great Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:46.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that will shortly be upon us,\N trash like you will not be needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:52.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those without magic power will be \Neliminated, and only wizards will be left alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A World of Great Magic, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:01.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only 10% of people in the world are wizards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:04.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The other 90% don't have any magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:09.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. In the World of Great \NMagic, those 90% cannot survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think we'll let you get away with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But what're they for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:19.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans who can't use magic are no better \Nthan a candle that can't be lit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They have no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:26.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in this world is here because \Nwe help one another to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:32.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Belcusas's attack from before \Nmust have injured his arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:35.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Help one another? Are you \Ntalking about guilds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:38.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:42.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are powerless. All \Nyou do is eat up resources!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:43.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:47.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We all need each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:52.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We bring the power, and the \Nnormal people pay the rewards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is built up from those requests...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:58.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how guilds were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:03.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare belittle guilds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:08.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you talk dirt about those \Nwizards struggling just to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:14.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you people cannot understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:17.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot get close to the \Ntrue depths of magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:21.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You, who do not know the \Ntrue terror of Zeref.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:25.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When Zeref shows his true power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:31.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be able to do nothing, nothing, \Nnothing except grovel before him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:34.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail will never bow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:39.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're a giant candle that shines \Nlight down on the deepest darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:43.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as elegant as your name would suggest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:48.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:53.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Trash like you aren't needed \Nin the World of Great Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:54.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me trash if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:59.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll never forgive you \Ncalling my friends trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:02.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Man cannot let that stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:10.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:22.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The basics of a Take Over \Nis to know your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:25.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Nee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking this arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Blade of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:43.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In my left hand dwells a shield \Nof gold that defends against all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You underestimated me. \NI won't be beaten so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:53.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What I was really after was your glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:08:01.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The only people who can call me \Nthat are the Raijinshuu and Laxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:06.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time I'll let you do it, special.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:10.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can make sure the mouth \Nof someone who insults Fairy Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:13.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,never opens again by turning them into stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:14.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stone Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...psych!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:37.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't my Stone Eyes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:38.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the bodies of the \Ntwo loves in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:50.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I could not be moved, even a tad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite a fun act.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:55.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My magic is the power of imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ark of Embodiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:08.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything I wish for is immediately \Nembodied into reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:11.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magic is ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:15.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Making dreams incarnate is \Nnear the very basis of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:19.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, there are a number \Nof limits and conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An invincible, undefeated magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:25.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have never been beaten! Not even once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:32.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Dimguil's Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:40.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast these foolish Fairies with all \Nthat sadness, and return them to dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:47.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf...man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:04.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wasn't your partner, you \Nmight've become an S Class Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:09.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You might not've lost to a guy like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:14.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:18.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you were here that \NI made it this far, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:22.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:26.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter, into the distant darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:05.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:06.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:07.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:10.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still in a rough state.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:15.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? My scarf?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:17.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy fixed it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:20.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She also flipped your clothes back around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:23.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:27.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:36.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go sniffing a lady, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:40.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, what smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:45.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:48.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:49.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:53.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's smell kind of blends together \Nand I can't tell who is where.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:57.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Natsu... Who did you smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:59.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy I met on Galuna Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:04.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you recall this masked person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling himself Zalty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:10.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,he tried to work behind the scenes \Nin a dark plot to obtain Deliora,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:13.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,one of Zeref's Demons, from \Nits slumber on Galuna Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:17.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was defeated by Natsu and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:25.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's close!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There he goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Galuna Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:35.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:39.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This and that and this and that... \NIt was a pretty tough fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:44.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That Zancrow fellow said \Nsomething like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:47.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed he remembers the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:48.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's Natsu for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:54.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... in a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And no one's around...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:17.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know what they say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you eat meat you start craving sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:23.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured this might happen, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:26.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought ice cream with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:28.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:36.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Seems everyone's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:38.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Transport the injured to the \Ntents stretched out on the reef.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and treat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:42.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can deal with fixing the equipment later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:47.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you recall, but this man is Lahar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:53.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Captain of the 4th Enforcement and \NDetention Corps of the Reformed Magic Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:59.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He once took Jellal into custody \Nafter the Nirvana incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:05.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and is now leading the warships \Nwatching over Tenroujima.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:07.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be heading onto the island now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:09.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who can prepare for battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:12.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dranbalt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:18.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain once again who \Nthis man, Mest, really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:24.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He called himself Mest, but \Nhis real name is Dranbalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:29.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a member of the Reformed Magic \NCouncil's Intelligence Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:32.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is someone like you doing so injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:33.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:35.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:39.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to say we're fine, but \Nat least there were no casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the communications lacrima safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thankfully...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:44.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:49.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A three-way battle between \NFairy Tail, Grimoire Heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:52.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Black Wizard Zeref has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:56.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The attack on the ship before \Nwas from Grimoire Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me the communications lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to report this to \Nheadquarters right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:03.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:07.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three of the thorns in the side of the \NMagic World have all gathered in one place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:11.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The chances of this being \Ncoincidence are nearly zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:14.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gran Doma, the chairman, is strict
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:17.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and will not hesitate to eliminate \Nwrongdoers without even a trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:22.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he let fall the "Attack \Nof Sealed Light" once again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Etherion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:28.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we have no way to oppose \Nthe decisions of our superiors...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:33.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! It's true that Fairy Tail's \Nalways been at odds with the Council,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:36.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but they shouldn't be lumped in \Nwith Zeref and Grimoire Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:41.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not for us to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:51.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry and contact headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The World of Great Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:15.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone without magic will be eliminated?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a horrible world \Nwhere no one gains anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:26.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Hades has not informed \Nmeh of his true intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:29.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but perhaps it will be a land of \Nthose who know the depths of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref is on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:35.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When weh get our hands on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:38.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the world will beh enveloped \Nwith magic and reborn anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:45.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're prepared for the consequences \Nwhen you make a mess outta someone else's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:48.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meh orders are two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:52.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The first is to capture Zeref and \Nhand him over to Master Hades.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:56.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The second is to wipe out Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:59.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe us out? Just try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:00.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:03.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:07.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If he calls himself one \Nof the 7 Kin of Purgatory,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:10.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then we should assume there \Nare 6 more at his level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:14.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you, search for the other \NKin of Purgatory and defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:19.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even all 4 of us couldn't scratch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:22.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because of his magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:26.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An ancient magic... Human \NSubordination Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:29.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Human... Subordination?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:34.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's magic that allows you to command a \Nhuman's fighting power or magic for a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:36.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also known as the Magic of Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:40.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that magic won't work \Non me, a Celestial Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:45.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, you may have already realized \Nit, but he's also a Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:48.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Goat, Capricorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:50.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:55.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two Spirits fighting each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:02.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:03.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:10.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've requested a one-on-one match \Nbetween two Spirits, Capricorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:11.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:16.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had thought you'd completely forgotten \Nthat you were a Spirit, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:19.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:21.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough, but Loke's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:26.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're under his magic \Nspell, we can't fight for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave this to Loke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:28.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:32.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You could tell from the fight before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans can't beat this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:37.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if two Spirits are fighting \Neach other, I have to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:39.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:43.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare for him to raise his voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:46.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be some history here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:48.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Figure it out, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:52.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe in him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:59.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. I'm worried about the others. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:07.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to come back to me, you hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:17.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:23.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Regulus, give me the power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:36.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years has it been since you \Ndisappeared from the Spirit World?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,17 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:45.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To stay in the Human World that \Nlong... Who the hell is your master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:47.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is meh master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:50.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is meh who is the master of humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:53.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero of Rubenguard, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:57.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A gate to another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,San Jiao Shin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:11.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:15.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,During the civil war of Rubenguard in 779,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:20.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a young general, San Jiao \NShin, who led the rebel army to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The official records say he \Nwent missing after the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:27.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is that he \Nbecame meh subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:32.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He captured a human, and summoned him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:36.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let meh ask you about {\i1}your{\i0} master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:38.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:41.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that I can subordinate her, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:48.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already deduced that it's \Nthe blond woman who ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:50.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You want a one-on-one battle with meh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:51.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:57.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that to let your master \Nescape to a safe location.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:03.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits sure have to take \Nthe worst roles, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:07.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to come back to me, you hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:08.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:17.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure... to come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:19.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:25.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could it be... That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He realized!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:29.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're keeping her away from meh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:30.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping her away from meh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:33.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:38.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she Layla Heartfilia's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:42.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... He really figured it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:44.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let her live!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:46.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:49.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell it, I smell it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:50.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, can I ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:52.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.63,0:21:55.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to finish things \Nwith that guy from Galuna Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:57.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a point to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:22:00.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although his mask was pretty cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:01.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:04.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So by smell, do you mean the \Nsmell of sweat inside the mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:06.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:08.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, take this seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:15.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Zalty that Natsu has \Ngotten wind of is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:19.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:24.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.69,0:23:58.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two sheep... Er, two "people".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:23:59.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What about sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.89,0:24:01.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.01,0:24:04.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fluffy Spirit Lucy has is a sheep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.43,0:24:06.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aries? Right, a sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:09.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Loke also fighting a sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.07,0:24:10.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do Spirits have twins or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.81,0:24:13.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They are a bit similar, \Nbut this one's a goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.85,0:24:16.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Human Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:18.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.29,0:24:23.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Goats go "me~h", while sheep go "be~h".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.06,0:24:25.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I can't tell the difference at all.
